* ''[[Caritas in Veritate]]'', l'Amour dans la Vérité, [[encyclique]] [http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/benedict_xvi/encyclicals/documents/hf_ben-xvi_enc_20090629_caritas-in-veritate_fr.html (lire)], 2009;
